'''本蒂亚巴河'''（{{lang-pt|'''Bentiaba'''}}），或称圣尼古拉斯河（{{lang-pt|Rio de São Nicolau}}），是[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]西南部的一条河流，流入大西洋，河口位于[[纳米贝省|纳米贝省]]靠近{{link-pt|本蒂亚巴|Bentiaba}}处。

本蒂亚巴河岸堆积有许多白垩纪时期的化石，包括[[滄龍科|滄龍科]]动物。<ref>[https://www.academia.edu/2493354/New_mosasaur_material_from_the_Maastrichtian_of_Angola_with_notes_on_the_phylogeny_distribution_and_palaeoecology_of_the_genus_Prognathodon New mosasaur material from the Maastrichtian of Angola, with notes on the phylogeny, distribution and palaeoecology of the genus Prognathodon], Anne S. Schulp, Michael J. Polcyn, Octávio Mateus, Louis L. Jacobs, Maria Luísa Morais & Tatiana da Silva Tavares</ref>本蒂亚巴河也是一白垩纪骨层名称的来源。<ref>Strganac, C., Jacobs L., Polcyn M., Mateus O., Myers T., Araújo R., Fergunson K. M., Gonçalves A. O., Morais M. L., Schulp A. S., da Tavares T. S., & Salminen J. (2014).  Geological Setting and Paleoecology of the Upper Cretaceous Bench 19 Marine Vertebrate Bonebed at Bentiaba, Angola. Netherlands Journal of Geosciences. 1-16.</ref>

